    "For guaranteed alerts (Sentry/security) with the app closed, run the optional push microservice (see /server). Requires an Apple Push key. Without it, alerts are local-only while the app runs.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para avisos garantizados (Centinela/seguridad) con la app cerrada, ejecuta el microservicio de push opcional (ver /server). Requiere una clave de Apple Push. Sin él, los avisos son locales solo mientras la app está abierta."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "For guaranteed alerts (Sentry/security) with the app closed, run the optional push microservice (see /server). Requires an Apple Push key. Without it, alerts are local-only while the app runs."
          }
        }
      }
